longBusinessSummary: IceCure Medical Ltd develops and markets minimally invasive cryoablation therapies for women's health and oncology markets. It offers ProSense system, a cryoablation solution for breast tumors. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Caesarea, Israel.
